Acme-SvGROW version 0.01
========================

increase the memory allocated for the pv "string" side of a perl scalar, using a pure-perl technique.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

pure perl. L-value function requires a perl supporting lvalue subroutines.

